<div style="max-width: 800px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">
  <h1>📝 Form Demo</h1>

  <% if @processed_message %>
    <div style="background-color: #d4edda; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; border: 1px solid #c3e6cb; margin: 20px 0;">
      <h3 style="color: #155724;">✅ Form Processed!</h3>
      <p style="font-size: 1.2em; margin: 10px 0;"><%= @processed_message %></p>
      <p><strong>Original input:</strong> "<%= @user_input %>"</p>
    </div>
  <% end %>

  <div style="background-color: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin: 20px 0;">
    <%= form_with url: form_demo_path, method: :post, local: true do |f| %>
      <div style="margin-bottom: 15px;">
        <%= f.label :user_input, "Enter some text:", style: "display: block; margin-bottom: 5px; font-weight: bold;" %>
        <%= f.text_field :user_input,
            style: "width: 100%; padding: 10px; border: 1px solid #ddd; border-radius: 4px; font-size: 16px;",
            placeholder: "Type something here..." %>
      </div>
      <%= f.submit "Process Text",
          style: "background-color: #ffc107; color: black; padding: 12px 25px; border: none; border-radius: 5px; cursor: pointer; font-size: 16px;" %>
    <% end %>
  </div>

  <div style="background-color: #e9ecef; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0;">
    <h3>🔍 MVC Flow for Forms:</h3>
    <ol>
      <li><strong>GET Route:</strong> <code>get "form_demo"</code> displays the form</li>
      <li><strong>POST Route:</strong> <code>post "form_demo"</code> processes the form</li>
      <li><strong>Controller:</strong> Checks if <code>request.post?</code> to handle form submission</li>
      <li><strong>View:</strong> Shows form and conditionally displays results</li>
    </ol>
  </div>

  <div style="background-color: #d1ecf1; padding: 15px; border-radius: 5px; margin: 20px 0;">
    <h4>🎯 Key Concepts Demonstrated:</h4>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>HTTP Methods:</strong> GET to display form, POST to submit it</li>
      <li><strong>Form Helpers:</strong> Rails <code>form_with</code> helper generates the form</li>
      <li><strong>Parameter Handling:</strong> Form data comes through <code>params[:user_input]</code></li>
      <li><strong>Conditional Rendering:</strong> View shows different content based on controller logic</li>
      <li><strong>Same Route, Different Actions:</strong> Same URL can handle both GET and POST</li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <p>
    <strong>Current Request Method:</strong> <code><%= request.request_method %></code><br>
    <strong>Form Submitted:</strong> <%= request.post? ? "✅ Yes" : "❌ No" %>
  </p>

  <%= link_to "← Back to Demo Home", root_path,
      style: "background-color: #6c757d; color: white; padding: 10px 20px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 5px;" %>
</div>